steps.name: Click on the 'Contact' link from the sidebar menu
Click on the 'Client or prospect' drop-down field
Select the first option from the 'Client' drop-down list
Enter the first name of the contact
Enter the last name of the contact
Enter email address of the contact
Enter phone number of the contact
Click on the 'Create and return' button
